@Api_HostAddress = http://localhost:5129
@SessionId = 55555555-5555-5555-5555-555555555555
@CardId = 66666666-6666-6666-6666-666666666666

### Lessons Health
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lessons/health
Accept: application/json

###

### Create lesson (userId = external user Guid z modułu Users)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lessons?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "lessonKind": "flashcards",
  "wordCount": 20
}

###

### Dodaj wynik powtórzenia (lessonId z utworzonej lekcji; questionResultId = cards.results.id strony pytania)
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lessons/1/repetitions?userId=00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000001
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "questionResultId": 42,
  "result": true
}

###

### Get Next Lesson Card
GET {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lessons/next
Accept: application/json

###

### Submit Lesson Answer
POST {{Api_HostAddress}}/api/lessons/{{SessionId}}/answer
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: application/json

{
  "cardId": "{{CardId}}",
  "isCorrect": true,
  "userAnswer": "sample answer"
}
